{"article_id":"ofENZKEHODnLsyc2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 5:02","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Post Email","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Terms of Trade is a daily newsletter","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that untangles a world","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"embroiled in trade wars .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Sign up here .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump said","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"China wants to make a deal","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"as he praised comments by the country ' s chief negotiator for trade ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"offering a more conciliatory tone","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"after escalating tensions in recent days .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" They want to make a deal very badly , \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump said during a press conference from the Group of Seven meeting in Biarritz , France .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" The tariffs have hit them very hard . \"","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Trump also noted remarks","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"made earlier Monday by China ' s top trade negotiator , Vice Premier Liu He .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" He wants to see a deal made ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"he wants it to be made under calm conditions , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" He used the word ' calm , '","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I agree with him . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"U.S. stocks rallied Monday after optimistic remarks at the G-7 from Trump and French President Emmanuel Macron ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he saw a willingness for a U.S.-China trade deal .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The dollar strengthened","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and 10-year Treasury yields held close to a three-year low .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Liu said at the opening ceremony of the 2019 Smart China Expo in Chongqing :","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" We are willing to solve the problem through consultation and cooperation with a calm attitude , \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"according to a Caixin report .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" We firmly oppose the escalation of the trade war , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that it \" is not conducive to China , the U.S. and the interests of people all over the world . \"","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"While Trump mostly struck a conciliatory tone in his press conference ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"he also insisted","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that any deal would have to address the imbalance in trade .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"If it didn ' t ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the U.S. would stop doing business with China .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"\" This has to be a deal","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that ' s better for us , \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"\" And","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"if it ' s not better","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"I don ' t want to do business . \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Earlier Monday Trump said","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"the prospects for a deal with China are better now than at any time","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"since negotiations began last year ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"even as a top state-media editor in Beijing questioned his version of events .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"China last night called \" our trade people","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"let ' s get back to the table. \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"He also lauded President Xi Jinping as a \" great leader \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"\" anything ' s possible \"","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"when asked","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"if he would delay tariff increases on China .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"\" You can say we ' re having very meaningful talks , much more meaningful","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"than I would say at any time frankly , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"while meeting with German Chancellor Angela Merkel on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" Maybe I ' m wrong","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"but we ' re in a stronger position now","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to do a deal , a fair deal for everyone , \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Still , a spokesman for China ' s foreign ministry wasn ' t able to immediately confirm the details of the phone calls on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Later , Hu Xijin , editor-in-chief of China ' s Global Times newspaper , said in a tweet","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that top trade negotiators hadn ' t spoken by phone in recent days","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and that Trump was exaggerating the significance of the trade contacts .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"At the press conference , Trump answered questions on the discrepancy","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"insisting","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that there had been \" numerous calls \" over the past two days","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"including with U.S. Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Mnuchin , also in Biarritz , said earlier Monday","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"\" there were discussions","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"that went back and forth","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"and let ' s just leave it at that . \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Based on what I know ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Chinese and US top negotiators did n't hold phone talks in recent days .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"The two sides have been keeping contact at technical level ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"it does n't have significance","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that President Trump suggested .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"China did n't change its position .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"China wo n't cave to US pressure .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"- Hu Xijin 胡锡进","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"( @ HuXijin_GT )","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"August 26 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Trump ' s comments mark the latest twist in months of negotiations","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that have seen moments of optimism give way to even greater escalation .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"While the two sides have at times appeared close to a deal ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"China has balked at U.S. demands for market-based reforms in areas like state-run enterprises","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that could jeopardize the Communist Party ' s grip on power .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"\" China called last night our top trade people","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"let ' s get back to the table . \"","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Trump says","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"China wants to restart trade talks during a meeting with Egypt ' s President # G7Summit","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"pic.twitter.com/VWHjo4H1nA","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"- TicToc","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"( @ tictoc )","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"August 26 , 2019","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"The developments came","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"after a weekend of tit-for-tat tariffs had rocked financial markets","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"and fueled fears","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that the standoff would drag the global economy into recession .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Beijing ' s retaliation on Friday to an earlier U.S. tariff hike led to yet another increase from Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"who said","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that existing 25 % tariffs on some $ 250 billion in imports from China would rise to 30 % come Oct. 1 , the 70th anniversary of the founding of the People ' s Republic of China .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Morgan Stanley warned","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that the spiral of trade measures could result in a global downturn within nine months .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"China has consistently agreed to engage in talks","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"even with tariff escalations taking place .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"A round of negotiations","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that had been planned for September","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"had not formally been called off","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"after Trump pivoted to further tariff increases","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"even after an apparent detente between the two sides in Shanghai last month .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Great respect for the fact","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"that President Xi & his Representatives want \" calm resolution. \"","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"So impressed","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"that they are willing to come out","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"& state the facts so accurately .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"This is why he is a great leader","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"& representing a great country .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Talks are continuing !","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"https : //t.co/0sotrd1Mzh","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"August 26 , 2019","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"Trump tweeted over the weekend","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that the U.S. \" would be far better off \"","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"without China ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"and claimed","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"he could order U.S. businesses to withdraw from the country .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"China will follow through with retaliatory measures","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"announced Friday","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"and fight the trade war to the end ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"after the U.S. failed to keep its promises ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"the Communist Party flagship newspaper People ' s Daily wrote in a Saturday editorial .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Later , the Editor-in-Chief of the nationalist Global Times , Hu Xijin , said on Twitter","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"that the U.S. is \" starting to lose China .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"\" China has 'lost ' the US already :","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"all-round high tariffs , Huawei ban , political hostility , Hong Kong , Taiwan ...","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"We 're facing a completely different United States .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"We have nothing more to lose ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"while the US is just starting to lose China .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"- Hu Xijin 胡锡进","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"( @ HuXijin_GT )","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"August 24 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Trump ' s comments from Biarritz were met with skepticism in Beijing .","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"\" Trump pays great attention to the stock market ' s performance , \"","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"said Gai Xinzhe , non-resident research fellow at the China Institute for WTO Studies at the University of International Business and Economics in Beijing .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"\" Trump may want to use a vague description of the call","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"to stabilize the market sentiment","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"and ease pressure .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"We will see what happens next . \"","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"- With assistance by Miao Han , Josh Wingrove , Jeff Kearns , and Shawn Donnan","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":319,"left":167,"right":318,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":166,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":162,"right":165,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":1,"right":161,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","